00:04:14.254 --> 00:04:16.589 line:95%,end
And now, Chloe.

00:04:16.656 --> 00:04:19.058 line:95%,end
You had a great performance.

00:04:19.125 --> 00:04:21.828 line:95%,end
You went out on stage,
you looked beautiful,

00:04:21.894 --> 00:04:25.098 line:95%,end
your mom was beaming,
they announced you as the
winner.

00:04:25.465 --> 00:04:28.601 line:95%,end
EMCEE: Entry number 19
from Abby Lee Dance Company, You
Can!

00:04:29.002 --> 00:04:30.670 line:95%,end
ABBY LEE: The scores
were not right.

00:04:30.737 --> 00:04:32.605 line:95%,end
