00:04:42.949 --> 00:04:46.019 line:95%,end
And next, we have Asia.

00:04:46.085 --> 00:04:47.954 line:95%,end
Now, Asia is not here.

00:04:48.021 --> 00:04:50.123 line:95%,end
Asia will be back in
pyramid next week.

00:04:50.189 --> 00:04:53.259 line:5%,start
