is In10sity Dance.

00:05:12.912 --> 00:05:15.515 line:95%,end
Now, this week's assignments.

00:05:15.581 --> 00:05:17.784 line:95%,end
Maddie, you will be
doing a top solo.

00:05:17.850 --> 00:05:20.787 line:95%,end
[applause]

00:05:20.853 --> 00:05:22.255 line:5%,start
Maddie's solo this week is tap,

00:05:22.322 --> 00:05:23.823 line:5%,start
and she's going
to be so amazing,

00:05:23.890 --> 00:05:25.758 line:5%,start
