00:05:56.522 --> 00:05:59.525 line:95%,end
[applause]

00:05:59.926 --> 00:06:04.097 line:95%,end
I know that it's unfortunate,
the whole Maddie-Chloe solo
thing.

00:06:04.163 --> 00:06:05.598 line:95%,end
Mistakes happen.

00:06:05.665 --> 00:06:07.767 line:95%,end
I'm giving Chloe
another opportunity

00:06:07.834 --> 00:06:09.569 line:95%,end
