00:06:24.851 --> 00:06:26.386 line:95%,end
She's so unfair.

00:06:26.452 --> 00:06:30.556 line:95%,end
The group routine is
called Gone Too Soon.

00:06:31.090 --> 00:06:34.794 line:95%,end
And of course, we're referring
to all those Hollywood
tragedies.

00:06:35.661 --> 00:06:38.431 line:95%,end
Nia, you will portray
Whitney Houston.

00:06:40.600 --> 00:06:45.638 line:95%,end
Kendall, I want to see
the sass and spunk of Selena.

