the Grammy-winning Latin artist,
Selena.

00:06:55.214 --> 00:06:58.651 line:95%,end
Brooke will be inspired
by Amy Winehouse.

00:06:59.786 --> 00:07:01.020 line:95%,end
Ah!

00:07:01.087 --> 00:07:03.790 line:95%,end
