- The sea witch.

00:08:38.584 --> 00:08:41.420 line:95%,end
Oh. Ursula was the octopus.

00:08:41.487 --> 00:08:42.522 line:95%,end
The big black--

00:08:42.588 --> 00:08:45.625 line:95%,end
CHRISTI: She wears black and she
steals little beautiful
children's talent.

00:08:45.691 --> 00:08:46.692 line:95%,end
MELISSA: Isn't she?
