jar around her neck.

00:08:51.264 --> 00:08:52.965 line:95%,end
- CHRISTI: She steals talent.
- JILL: She's Ursula.

00:08:53.032 --> 00:08:54.834 line:95%,end
She is Ursula.

00:08:54.901 --> 00:08:56.869 line:95%,end
JILL: Oh, golly.

00:08:57.470 --> 00:08:59.438 line:5%,start
ABBY LEE: Hello.
Are you ready for hip-hop?

00:09:00.439 --> 00:09:01.474 line:5%,start
