you better be able to be a hip
-hop dancer.

00:09:14.453 --> 00:09:16.489 line:5%,start
[music playing]

00:09:16.556 --> 00:09:20.826 line:95%,end
So Chloe is doing a hip-hop
routine entitled beautiful.

00:09:20.893 --> 00:09:24.830 line:95%,end
It's more of a jazz routine
with hip-hop elements,

00:09:24.897 --> 00:09:27.199 line:95%,end
hip-hop costume, hip-hop style.

00:09:28.100 --> 00:09:30.703 line:95%,end
I want her to succeed
with this hip-hop routine.

00:09:30.770 --> 00:09:32.338 line:95%,end
And I'm bringing Payton in.

